title: DAZ3D - Ajax Hair for Genesis 3 Male
description:
Ajax Hair for Genesis 3 Male
----------------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/3fcd0c411536e7c1ae246296070d77e5.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/34231

Ajax Hair is a morphing, polygonal model of long, messy, wavy hair. The hair is fitted for Genesis 3 Male(s) (.DUF) with auto-conforming custom morphs for Daz Original characters. Iray and 3Delight material presets for various texture map colors are included plus diffuse color setting samples. The diffuse color samples show how you can easily create your own tints by changing the diffuse color of the hair
